self can have an\nimpact in shaping the ICM thermo-dynamical structure and ultimately in the use\nof SPH cluster simulations for cosmological studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Oct 2014 20:00:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
