ple to show that the scheme fails in dimension $6$ (and\nabove).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Oct 2014 21:31:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Nov 2014 15:42:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 20 Nov 2014 13:40:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 9 Sep 2015 13:51:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-24"}
